Download Groovy from the below url
https://groovy.jfrog.io/ui/native/dist-release-local/groovy-zips/apache-groovy-binary-3.0.9.zip
Unzip/Extract to the local file system or folder
Set the Groovy Installation path in Environment Variables 
Environment Variables --- Path ---- Edit --- New --- (E:\Softwares\apache-groovy-sdk-3.0.8\groovy-3.0.8\bin) Copy the groovy Installation path -- Ok -- Ok 
Go to Command Prompt verify groovy version 
C:\Users\QC>groovy -version
Groovy Version: 3.0.8 JVM: 1.8.0_241 Vendor: Oracle Corporation OS: Windows 10

